# xpatcher authentication
#
# Option 1: Anthropic API key (from https://platform.claude.com)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...
#
# Option 2: Leave this file empty or remove it to use your Claude
# subscription (Pro/Max/Team/Enterprise). xpatcher will automatically
# extract OAuth credentials from your logged-in Claude Code session.
#
# To log in: run `claude` interactively and complete the login flow.
